\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"io_util\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Severe response time degradation with rrt and rrt_max showing massive increases (197-198x median change ratio)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-2: rrt from 1362.2 to 283515.09 (197.9x), rrt_max from 9424.0 to 1514016.0 (159.7x)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend service pods\",\n      \"reason\": \"All frontend pods (frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2) experienced significant rrt and rrt_max increases\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: rrt 12033.29→197093.3 (16.4x), rrt_max 216419→1604757 (7.4x); frontend-1: rrt 12069.42→193921.34 (16.1x), rrt_max 237946→1608371 (6.8x)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice pods\",\n      \"reason\": \"Multiple shippingservice pods showing client_error_ratio and error_ratio spikes to 42.5-47.5%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-1: error_ratio 0.0→47.5%; shippingservice-2: error_ratio 0.0→42.5%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice pods\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice-0 and cartservice-1 showing high error ratios around 35-38%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-0: error_ratio 0.0→38.36%; cartservice-1: error_ratio 0.0→35.29%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Client error ratio spike from 0% to 8.16%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice-2: client_error_ratio 0.0→8.16%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"IO utilization showing changes with io_util metric\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-tikv: io_util p99 change from 0.07 to 0.04\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Key Findings:**\n1. **cartservice-2** is the most severely affected component with response time degradation of nearly 200x\n2. **Frontend service** is experiencing cascading performance issues across all pods\n3. **Error rates** are significantly elevated in shippingservice and cartservice pods\n4. The issue appears to be a service-level performance degradation rather than infrastructure-level (no Node resource issues detected)\n\nThe root cause appears to be a cascading failure starting with cartservice-2, which then impacted the frontend services and caused increased error rates across multiple services."}
